und online or by fax email or postal mail online the fastest way to receive your refund is to log into your student account and drop your course online fax send a fax to 650 725 4248 email send an email to continuingstudies drop stanford edu please allow up to two weeks to process emailed or faxed refunds on your credit card refunds by check may take up to four weeks to process if you have recently submitted a drop request please wait at least 72 hours before contacting our office with any questions or issues no refunds will be given after the deadline unless continuing studies program cancels the course registration begins february 27 8 30 am pst first week of classes apr 2 call 650 725 2650 or continuingstudies stanford edu 2012 stanford university all rights reserved home site map university policies mla program instructor login help
